<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA57">
<l>nīyulaka mellā mirappiṉu niṉṉuṭaiya</l>
<l>tīya varavoḻiyac celkaṇṭāy - tūya</l>
<l>maṭavaralār vantu paliyiṭā rañci</l>
<l>viṭavarava mēlāṭa mikku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if you beg in the whole world, go, see,</l>
<l>while leaving behind the evil snakes you possess, as pure</l>
<l>women will not come [and] put offerings [before you]</l>
<l>while poisonous snakes are much dancing on [you].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
